title: SET_ENTITY_ROUTING_BUCKET
content:
0x635E5289// SetEntityRoutingBucket
void SET_ENTITY_ROUTING_BUCKET(Entity entity, int bucket);Parameters:entity: The entity to set the routing bucket for.bucket: The bucket ID.Sets the routing bucket for the specified entity.Routing buckets are also known as 'dimensions' or 'virtual worlds' in past echoes, however they are population-aware.
